Modifications
-------------
Changes made to the vendored sources include: repackaging as an autolinked
React Native library, a thin facade (`com.example.meshchat.sdk` /
`MeshChatSdk.swift`) and RN bridge, a private BLE service/characteristic UUID,
background/foreground-service and notification handling, power tuning, and
exposure of Noise private messaging + peer verification. See the git history
for details.
